@1003 = ~They do NOT! Pfft.~
@1004 = ~Uhm, I don't know about that. See, woolens are better, because I don't have to think about the poor rabbit or  squirrel that died for me to have them. I mean, shearing must be unpleasant for the sheep, but it's not as lethal as being skinned.~
@1005 = ~Hey, that's a great idea!~
@1006 = ~Excuse me, Mister?! I'm not that kind of girl! Besides, I can't cast spells very well if you clutch my pinkie, can I?~
@1007 = ~Sheesh, I didn't know that pirates go around hand in hand!~
@1008 = ~All the time.~
@1009 = ~(Wink) It's a cover-up.~
