@1054 = ~It's nice to hear.~
@1055 = ~Wow, now that came like a bolt out of the blue! (Wink.)~
@1056 = ~I love you too!~
@1057 = ~Ouf! That reminds me of that time when I read the Wall of Wind scroll!~
@1058 = ~You see, I didn't want to be discovered, so I thought I'd cast it inside a chest. Well, it tore the lid right off!~
@1059 = ~(Peony's unusual hair and the skirts of her robes become airborne with the motion, but she doesn't seem to care.)~
@1060 = ~(As you set her on the ground, she takes your hands into hers, sets her little booted feet, and leads you into a few more mad, whirling circles.)~
@1061 = ~(Squinting with pleasure, she throws her head back and laughs in an excited, tinkling way.)~
@1062 = ~Whoa! Oh, please, do it again! Pretty please?~
@1063 = ~(Peony nestles herself in your arms.)~
@1064 = ~Ahh, can we just... stay here?~
@1065 = ~You're not getting away with just a hug, Mister!~
@1066 = ~Kiss! Kiss! Ki... (A huge kiss.)~
@1067 = ~(She presses her cheek against your chest and sighs contentedly.)~
@1068 = ~Boom. Boom. Boom. I like your heartbeat!~
@1069 = ~(Peony throws her arms around your neck and looks up at you with shiny eyes.)~
@1070 = ~Mmgh...sweet! ~
@1071 = ~Heh, I wonder are there any salty kisses? Aha, I know! The kisses when lovers part. Tears and kisses, that's got to taste salty. Not that I want to sample it!~
@1072 = ~Must you distract me with this foolishness when I am trying so hard to stay *focused*?!~
@1073 = ~You bet! Being focused is waaaay too boring!~
@1074 = ~(Giggles.) You can't stop at just one!~
@1075 = ~Oh! You're such a good kisser!~
@1076 = ~Almost, almo- (Peony stops to breathe for a heart-beat.)~
@1077 = ~Nope, that's not it. Your poor little nose... (She strokes it gently with her finger.)~
@1078 = ~Sweetie, you're never going to get it right. Your nose is just too tiny. Why won't you stick with what you do best?~
@1079 = ~(She kisses you on the lips.) See, you're such a good kisser!~
@1080 = ~I'll let you know that this is a special Gnomish caress, and you're doing it all wrong - But, huh, who cares!~
