@1106 = ~Careful, careful! That's my very valuable main casting hand!~
@1107 = ~Oh, I wonder who taught you to say all these sweet things that make my heart melt.~
@1108 = ~You... well, you didn't brighten mine, because let's face it, it was very colorful to start with, but I really like having you in it.~
@1109 = ~Really?! I thought your life was not boring... being a pirate and all!~
@1110 = ~I'm glad if I did.~
@1111 = ~Oh, thank you. I hope you meant it as a compliment!~
@1112 = ~There's none like you either. Or at least there wasn't last time I checked.~
@1113 = ~Tee-hee, you missed the good part! Nobody is sweet, beautiful and smart like me!~
@1114 = ~You bet!~
@1115 = ~Yep, and you... my, but you've grown! From the scrawny kid kicked out by his big-shot paladin dad into a real hero! You and I are just wow!~
@1116 = ~Tee-hee, I expect Mystra to show up any day now and pick me as her tenth Chosen!~
@1117 = ~You've seen nothing yet, Mister!~
@1118 = ~Oh, nice! But must you sound exactly like grandma would?~
@1119 = ~Sure, the sort where you're doomed to love me forever and ever!~
@1120 = ~Do you think that if I'm an illusionist than everything I do is an illusion, even the most importan-~
@1121 = ~He-he! Sorry, I just can't keep up this serious tirade. Sweetie, I love you, and you know your own heart better than anyone else.~
@1122 = ~I think... I think it is an illusion.~
@1123 = ~I'll have to search my feelings then. ~
@1124 = ~You do that, and be thorough! I don't like that 'Peony, did you put a spell on me'? business. Nope, I don't like it at all.~
