@1144 = ~I know! I know! A naked frolicking incubus from the Abyss!~
@1145 = ~(Peony immediately sets her little feet on top of yours.)~
@1146 = ~Here we go, now you can do the walking for me!~
@1147 = ~(Peony leans her head back until she's able to look into your face and gives you a bright smile.)~
@1148 = ~(Soft and rounded, her bottom rests against you.)~
@1149 = ~(Her closeness causes a pleasant warmth to spread through your body.)~
@1150 = ~That's it! I'm going to spank you tonight till you can't sit down!~
@1151 = ~Eeeeik! Careful there, I don't have a spare one!~
@1152 = ~You, Mister, are an imp!~
@1153 = ~(The petite but well-defined subject of you attentions moves promptly out of reach.)~
@1154 = ~Mmgh... I really like the way you breathe.~
@1155 = ~Oh! Soooo sweet...~
@1156 = ~(Your lips are mercilessly tickled as you finish the kiss.)~
@1157 = ~(Your nose and lips submerge into the warm flowery midst of her hair and the cold, unforgiving outside world retreats for a moment.)~
@1158 = ~(She giggles.) How can such big hands be so gentle? It's some sort of a natural mystery.~
@1159 = ~(She covers your hand with hers.) You're so cute!~
@1160 = ~(Peony gives the base of your thumb a couple of tender kisses.)~
@1161 = ~(She rubs her cheek against your palm a bit and smiles dreamily.)~
@1162 = ~Pardon me?~
@1163 = ~Darling, I've never doubted that you continue to adore me. That you have been doing so quietly was to your advantage, really.~
@1164 = ~How pathetic is that? But of course, darling, go ahead. He'd let you mount him easily enough, after all it's his only chance.~
@1165 = ~If you are willing to associate with this brat, there is no helping you, darling. You two deserve one another.~
@1166 = ~Out of all the pathetic ways to save face you had to choose the quintessential one.~
@1167 = ~Are you quite finished? My patience is wearing thin.~
@1168 = ~(Salomeya is murmuring some tune sotto voice, with a mocking smile on her lips.)~
@1169 = ~Have you ever praised someone?~
@1170 = ~Do you ever tire of being a bitch?~
@1171 = ~Why do you think you're so darn special?~
@1172 = ~What do you think of me?~
@1173 = ~Sing for me, Salomeya.~
@1174 = ~You're such a tease! I'm sure that you like me.~
@1175 = ~Please, stop pushing me away. I want to help you overcome your bitterness.~
